WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.652
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.652 --> 00:00:04.957
Welcome to Unit 2, Good Neighbours and Jobs.

3
00:00:04.957 --> 00:00:09.087
This unit has 21 vocabulary cards in 4 learning groups.

4
00:00:09.087 --> 00:00:11.979
Group 1 is People in Your Neighbourhood.

5
00:00:11.979 --> 00:00:17.349
Listen for words such as neighbour, window cleaner, police officer, reporter, bus driver.

6
00:00:17.349 --> 00:00:19.827
Group 2 is Jobs and Equipment.

7
00:00:19.827 --> 00:00:24.371
Listen for words such as firefighter, helmet, boots, gloves, mask, uniform.

8
00:00:24.371 --> 00:00:27.675
Group 3 is More Jobs in the Community.

9
00:00:27.675 --> 00:00:31.806
Listen for words such as doctor, nurse, teacher, farmer, shopkeeper.

10
00:00:31.806 --> 00:00:35.110
Group 4 is Action Words (verb + ing).

11
00:00:35.110 --> 00:00:39.241
Listen for words such as helping, teaching, rescuing, growing, driving.

12
00:00:39.241 --> 00:00:49.568
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

13
00:00:49.568 --> 00:00:52.459
You are ready to begin Unit 2.
